reviews.text:
Too many people. People who did not buy starbucks drink also sitting there. People using extension plugs too. Sacarstic.

New drink, Sea Breeze Mint Chocolate Coffee FrappuccinoÂ® (Less Sweet), taste is really less sweet. Not much mint taste too.

Staff here are very friendly, and the service is excellent. The cuppa and bake are good as usual, too! There is also a good selection of plant-based milks to choose fromâ€”soy milk, oat milk, and coconut milk. ðŸŒ±

Had a cup of hot american brewed here while waiting for my student to arrive for tuition. I stayed here between 5:30 to 7:30pm, while there are always quite a few free seats, so this is a quite ideal place for everyone who wants to study/work in a cafe. Staff are friendly and efficient, the coffee they prepared are quite nice. The location is also fantastic, just the first store to see after walking out of mrt, or one level up from the bus interchange
Convenient location inside Clementi Mall, near to the MRT station. Space is a bit small and always no seats unless on a non-peak weekday. Coffee is good. Staff is very friendly.

I know people come here to chat with friends but no matter what if you are disturbing others around you and have been told twice to lower your volume, you should just be considerate!!! Not to mention this person didnt even order any drinks and sat here for 2 hours and disturbing others!!! Starbucks do better to manage your customers please!!!!!!!!
